title: Art Smart Game
description:
Art Smart Game developed from various artworks from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Are you art smart?  Exercise and strengthen your cultural awareness with our game.  Experience 52 cards comprising a set of 2 cards for each of 26 artists or cultures (e.g. Vasily Kandinsky, Vincent van Gogh, Claude Monet, Mary Cassatt and many more.)

Collect 2 different artwork cards from the same artist or culture to form pairs.  The player with the largest number of pairs win! For 2 or more players.

  • Card Dimensions: 3.75 x 5 in.
  • Box Dimensions: 4.25 x 5.5 in.
  • Box has magnetic closure.
